author: Play On Tabletop
description:
Battlefield about to get bloody brought to you by Miniwargaming and I Demo games upcoming Kickstarter, Trenches of Perdition http://MiniWarGaming.com/perdition 

Angron faces off against the Lion as the Dark Expansion continues. Jordan is back, after stepping on more legos, to face Tak with an elite Dark Angels force. How many named Warriors will make it out of this one? Lists below in the description.

Dark Expansion is a mini-series involving Imperium Forces challenging Chaos' reign on Imperium Nihilus. Brought to you with support from the many people who took part in our Dark Expansion fundraiser. As part of the campaign supporters had a chance to name a warrior in these battles. In these inter-connected games named warriors, if they survive, will make it to the final battle but those that perish are gone forever. The rise and fall of heroes!
